ength Range: Emits a captivating signal between 500nm and 600nm, making resistance nearly impossible.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Exceptional Results: Trapping and Eliminating Pests with Mastery</em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wide Coverage: Outstanding Performance.</li>\r\n	<li>Astounding Pest Capture: Within just 15 days, a remarkable number of 7,333 insects are effectively trapped in the highly infested or depends on&nbsp; pest density in the fields.</li>\r\n	<li>Demonstrating Superior Ability: Highlights the trap&rsquo;s exceptional effectiveness against threatening pests.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>DOSAGE:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>For Identification</td>\r\n			<td>1 Sheet / acre</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>For Monotoring &amp; Control</td>\r\n			<td>10 Sheets / acre</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>RECOMMENDED CROP:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For all crop cultivation.</p>\r\n', '<p>HOW TO USE ?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/1-Peal-256x300.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:256px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>STEP 1: Remove the traps from the polythene bag and carefully peel apart each other to expose the sticky area.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/2-Insert-Stick-163x300.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:163px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>STEP 2: Use wooden stick or thread or twist-ties to install sticky trap.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/3-Place-233x300.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:233px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>STEP 3: Place the traps just above the plant foliage. Adjust the height as the plants grow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/4-Greenhouse-233x300.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:233px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>STEP 4: In greenhouses, additionally use near vents and doors for better monitoring.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In taller crops &ndash; hung the sticky traps under the canopy of plant and or 5 ft above the ground level, where the sheet is exposed to light sufficiently.</li>\r\n	<li>Upon contact sticky material can be removed by cooking oil or any mineral oil.</li>\r\n	<li>For plants grown on benches, the sheets may be laid horizontally on the bench.</li>\r\n	<li>Carry out regular checking as and when required for identification of pest variety, counting if necessary, for its abundance and its developmental stages to take corrective pest management actions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>NOTE:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Keep away from children and domestic animals</li>\r\n	<li>Avoid direct contact with skin</li>\r\n	<li>Protective gloves recommended while handling</li>\r\n	<li>Buyer assumes all responsibility for safety and use in accordance with the directions</li>\r\n	<li>If you can spot isolated hot spots early you may need to spray to that small area only.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 1, '2023-11-18 08:43:08', 1, '2023-12-26 11:10:18', 1, 3, 1),
(40, 15, 'Barrix Magic Sticker Chromatic Trap - White Sheet (Pack of 50)', 'arsk white', '1209', 0, 'Attracts and traps 14 types of high risk sucking pests like Locust migratoria, Altica chalybea, Phyllotreta cruciferae, Nezara viridula etc.\r\nRecommended for all crop cultivation, protects your crops 24/7.\r\nAmazing monitoring tool to identify pest attack in the initial stages and effective in controlling as well.\r\nEasy to installation and use.\r\nReplace Sheets once filled with pests.\r\nSun & Heat Proof.\r\nRain Water Proof.\r\nScientifically researched colour alluring technology for pest attraction.\r\n\r\nNon Drying\r\n\r\n\r\nNon Driping\r\n\r\n\r\nResistance to high Temperature\r\n\r\n\r\nWaterproof\r\n\r\n\r\nDouble Sided Gumming\r\n\r\n\r\nAttracts more flies\r\n\r\n\r\n1\"x1\" grid for easy counting\r\nColor Alluring Technology:\r\nCutting-Edge Technology for Pest Control: Barrix Magic Sticker White Sheet\r\n\r\nThe Barrix Magic Sticker White Sheet revolutionizes pest control with cutting-edge technology that harnesses the natural behaviors and preferences of target pests. By understanding what attracts these pests, the sheet employs innovative color alluring technologies, optimizing color frequencies to irresistibly entice the identified pest families.\r\n\r\nStrategic color frequencies on the sheet mimic vital cues such as food sources, mating signals, or favorable habitats, effectively trapping pests by capitalizing on their natural instincts. This precise approach ensures efficient and targeted pest control, making the Barrix Magic Sticker White Sheet an exceptional trap.', '<p>DOSAGE:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>For Identification</td>\r\n			<td>1 Sheet / acre</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>For Monotoring &amp; Control</td>\r\n			<td>10 Sheets / acre or 25 sheets per hectare</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>RECOMMENDED CROP:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For all crop cultivation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Patanga-succinata.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Patanga succinata</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Locusta-migratoria.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Locusta migratoria</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Nomadacris-septemfasciata.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nomadacris septemfasciata</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Phyllotreta-downsei.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phyllotreta downsei</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Epitrix-cucumeris.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Epitrix cucumeris</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Altica-chalybea.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Altica chalybea</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Scirtothrips-dorsalis.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Scirtothrips dorsalis</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Stenchaetothrips-biformis.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stenchaetothrips biformis</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-Sheet-Sucking-Pest-Phyllotreta-cruciferae.png\" style=\"height:300px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phyllotreta cruciferae</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://barrix.in/images/2023/07/Barrix-Magic-Sticker-White-