light.</li>\r\n	<li>To remove sticky material from hands, use cooking oil or any mineral oil.</li>\r\n	<li>For plants grown on benches, lay the sheets horizontally on the bench.</li>\r\n	<li>Regularly check for pests, identify them, and count their abundance and developmental stages.</li>\r\n	<li>Take appropriate pest management actions based on the findings.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Caution:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Keep away from children and domestic animals</li>\r\n	<li>Avoid direct contact with skin</li>\r\n	<li>Protective gloves recommended while handling</li>\r\n	<li>Buyer assumes all responsibility for safety and use in accordance with the directions</li>\r\n	<li>If isolated hot spots are spotted early, advatage of using this product helps to consider spraying only that specific area.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 1, '2023-11-18 08:48:27', 1, '2023-12-26 11:18:41', 1, 3, 1);
